0.text: Asennie no kyerɛ ɛda a ɔbɛdi nnipa wɔabɔ no kwaadu no asɛm no.

1.text: Nnɛ no, na mframa wɔ bɛyɛ 83 km/h, na wɔhwɛ kwan ɛbɛkɔ so ara ago.

2.text: Akwaa titire a ɛwɔ circuatory sistɛm mu ne akoma no, a ɛno ɛpɔpe mmogya no.

3.text: Saa wɛbsaete weinom anya asrafoɔ pa ara, titiriw deɛ ɛfa nhomasua ho.

4.text: Nnipakuw nsrahwԑ bo yԑ fo, enti sԑ ԑyԑ wo pԑ anaasԑ wo ne adamfo baako pԑ no, bͻ mmͻden sԑ mobehyia nnipa afoforo na moayԑ kuw a nnipa anan kosi nsia wom ama ͻbaakofo bo aba fam.

5.text: Kamɛra no bi de 6 by 6 cm format na edi dwuma, sɛ yɛbɛka no yiye a 56 by 56 mm negative.

6.text: Yɛ wo nsiakyibaa nhyehyɛe no ne wɔn ho nsɛm a ɛbɛma wo nsa aka wɔn no sɛso pii fa hyɛ wo ho.

7.text: Fa kɔfe a ɛyɛ papa hyɛ wo fi ma anɔpa no ne chamomile tii a ɛdwodwo no anadwo no.

8.text: Asukɔtwea anaa nsukyenee a esian no nyɛ ade a ɛyɛ hu; mmeae a eisan no tumi som kakra, na afei nea ɛboro so no asian abegu fam.

9.text: Akatua ho towtua no da nso wɔ aman ahorow so, ɛnna towtua ho nhyehyɛe no nso da nso wɔ aman ahorow so.

1.text: Nnɛ no, na mframa wɔ bɛyɛ 83 km/h, na wɔhwɛ kwan ɛbɛkɔ so ara ago.

2.text: Akwaa titire a ɛwɔ circuatory sistɛm mu ne akoma no, a ɛno ɛpɔpe mmogya no.

3.text: Saa wɛbsaete weinom anya asrafoɔ pa ara, titiriw deɛ ɛfa nhomasua ho.

4.text: Nnipakuw nsrahwԑ bo yԑ fo, enti sԑ ԑyԑ wo pԑ anaasԑ wo ne adamfo baako pԑ no, bͻ mmͻden sԑ mobehyia nnipa afoforo na moayԑ kuw a nnipa anan kosi nsia wom ama ͻbaakofo bo aba fam.

5.text: Kamɛra no bi de 6 by 6 cm format na edi dwuma, sɛ yɛbɛka no yiye a 56 by 56 mm negative.

6.text: Yɛ wo nsiakyibaa nhyehyɛe no ne wɔn ho nsɛm a ɛbɛma wo nsa aka wɔn no sɛso pii fa hyɛ wo ho.

7.text: Fa kɔfe a ɛyɛ papa hyɛ wo fi ma anɔpa no ne chamomile tii a ɛdwodwo no anadwo no.

8.text: Asukɔtwea anaa nsukyenee a esian no nyɛ ade a ɛyɛ hu; mmeae a eisan no tumi som kakra, na afei nea ɛboro so no asian abegu fam.

9.text: Akatua ho towtua no da nso wɔ aman ahorow so, ɛnna towtua ho nhyehyɛe no nso da nso wɔ aman ahorow so.
